    "Without it, the game can't work.\nNo location = no map = no fun.\n\nWe promise we only use it during the game!": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Without it, the game can't work.\nNo location = no map = no fun.\n\nWe promise we only use it during the game!"
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Sans elle, le jeu ne fonctionne pas.\nPas de localisation = pas de carte = pas de fun.\n\nPromis, on ne l'utilise que pendant la partie !"
          }
        },
        "nl": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Zonder kan het spel niet werken.\nGeen locatie = geen kaart = geen plezier.\n\nWe beloven dat we het alleen tijdens het spel gebruiken!"
