    "Keep it secret: share it only with the referee.": {
      "comment": "Helper text under the 4-digit GameMaster password input.",
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Garde-le secret : tu le partages seulement à l'arbitre."
          }
        },
        "nl": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Houd hem geheim: deel hem alleen met de scheidsrechter."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "The designated hunter becomes the chicken; they leave the hunters list. Only possible before the game starts.": {
      "comment": "Explanation footer for the GameMaster's designate-the-chicken action.",
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Le chasseur désigné devient la poule ; il quitte la liste des chasseurs. Possible uniquement avant le début de la partie."
          }
        },
        "nl": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "De aangewezen jager wordt de kip; hij verlaat de jagerslijst. Alleen mogelijk vóór het begin van het spel."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "%@ will become the chicken. The current chicken will lose this role.": {
      "comment": "Confirmation alert body when GameMaster designates a new chicken. %@ is the new chicken's team name.",
      "localizations": {
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "%@ deviendra la poule. La poule actuelle perdra ce rôle."
          }
        },
        "nl": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "%@ wordt de kip. De huidige kip verliest deze rol."
